{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-past-activities/task-1","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 1","description":"","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Poslušaj zvuk i dovrši rečenicu ispod.</p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Wakati wa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Present Perfect</span> koristi se za razgovor o radnjama ili iskustvima koja su se dogodila u nekom trenutku pre sadašnjosti.</p>\n<p>Koristi ovu strukturu da pričaš o nečemu što se desilo pre sada, ali <strong>gde realno vreme nije uzete u obzir</strong>.</p>\n<p>Da biste kreirali vreme za <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Present Perfect</span>, koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">have</span> ili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">has</span> praćeno starim glagolskim oblikom.</p>\n<p>Arhaični oblik glagola <span class=\"highlighted-text\">see</span> je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">seen</span>. On je neobičan, jer se njegovo značenje/konjugacija ne sastoji samo od <span class=\"highlighted-text\">-ed</span> kao što to rade uobičajeni glagoli. Primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">I have seen the report.</span> - Nekada pre toga, našli ste izveštaj.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">She has seen the report.</span> - Nekada pre, on je primetio izveštaj.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"English","superBlock":"b1-english-for-developers","block":"learn-how-to-talk-about-past-activities","lang":"en-US","fields":{"slug":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-past-activities/task-1"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>Have you BLANK the latest user feedback?</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"seen","feedback":"<p>Raniji glagol od <span class=\"highlighted-text\">see</span> nije uobičajen, niti je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">see</span> ni <span class=\"highlighted-text\">saw</span>.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"interview-room3.png","characters":[{"character":"James","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"B1_3-1.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":0,"finishTimestamp":2.76},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"James","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"James","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":3.76,"dialogue":{"text":"Have you seen the latest user feedback?","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"James","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":4.26,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/#learn-how-to-talk-about-past-activities","dashedName":"task-1","certification":"b1-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"b1-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-how-to-talk-about-past-activities","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-past-activities/task-2","prevChallengePath":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-past-activities/dialogue-1-the-latest-user-feedback","id":"66c8e6cdd7a69d2878880fbf","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":19,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-past-activities/task-1"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}